OL,3,CEx-partner jailed for 20 years for
OL,4,CAlyson Nelson murder
OL,6,FA pensioner who stabbed his former
OL,7,Fpartner seven times in her Co Antrim
OL,8,Fhome in a jealous rage has been jailed
OL,9,Ffor 20 years.
OL,11,FWilliam Finlay gave no reaction in the
OL,12,Fdock as the Judge handed down his
OL,13,Fsentence.
OL,15,FThe 68-year-old pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Fmurdering retired nurse Alyson Nelson
OL,17,Fin a 'premeditated and vicious' attack
OL,18,Fin the mother-of-four's Whitehead home
OL,19,Fin April 2022.
