OL,4,CAlyson Nelson murder
OL,6,FThe 64-year-old met Finlay online but
OL,7,Fended the relationship in 2020.
OL,9,FEighteen months later Finlay, of Old
OL,10,FForde Gardens in Whitehead, decided to
OL,11,Fmurder her because he was jealous of
OL,12,Fher new relationship.
OL,14,FThe judge said CCTV captured Finlay
OL,15,Fgoing to her home on the night of
OL,16,FApril 16 2022, where he stabbed her a
OL,17,Fnumber of times in a "vicious,
OL,18,Funrelenting attack".
