OL,4,CAlyson Nelson murder
OL,6,FThe Public Prosecution Service said
OL,7,Fthe murder of Alyson Nelson was a
OL,8,F"shocking and violent attack" on a
OL,9,Fdefenceless victim.
OL,11,FWilliam Finlay has been told he will
OL,12,Fserve a minimum of 20 years of a life
OL,13,Fsentence after being convicted of the
OL,14,Fmurder of his former partner in April
OL,15,F2022.
OL,17,FPPS senior public prosecutor Keith
OL,18,FHarbinson said: "Finlay went armed
OL,19,Fwith a knife from his kitchen to Ms
OL,20,FNelson's house early on the evening of
OL,21,FApril 16 2022.
