OL,6,F"He carried out a shocking and violent
OL,7,Fattack on his defenceless victim in
OL,8,Fher own home, stabbing her seven times
OL,9,Fin less than a minute.
OL,11,F"The Police Service of Northern
OL,12,FIreland investigation uncovered
OL,13,Fextensive evidence including the knife
OL,14,FFinlay used, forensic and witness
OL,15,Fevidence, and footage from a doorbell
OL,16,Fcamera at Ms Nelson's home.
