OL,6,F"This footage showed the defendant
OL,7,Farriving at the house in Victoria
OL,8,FAvenue and leaving a minute later,
OL,9,Fwiping down the knife he had used to
OL,10,Fstab her.
OL,12,F"The prosecution team including senior
OL,13,Fcounsel worked collaboratively with
OL,14,Fpolice, using the evidence they
OL,15,Fgathered to build a compelling case
OL,16,Ffor court against Finlay, which led to
OL,17,Fhis guilty plea in November 2023.
OL,19,F"Finlay murdered Ms Nelson following
OL,20,Fthe end of their relationship."
