OL,6,FDetective Inspector Michelle Griffin
OL,7,Fhas welcomed the sentencing of William
OL,8,FFinlay for the murder of Alyson
OL,9,FNelson, describing it as the first for
OL,10,Fmurder aggravated by domestic abuse
OL,11,Fsince new legislation became law in
OL,12,F2022.
OL,14,FSpeaking outside Belfast Crown Court,
OL,15,Fshe said: "Today he was told he will
OL,16,Fserve a minimum of 20 years in prison.
