OL,4,CAlyson Nelson murder
OL,6,F"Alyson Nelson, who was 64 years old,
OL,7,Fwas attacked by William Finlay on
OL,8,FSaturday, April 16, 2022. She was
OL,9,Fstabbed multiple times in her own home
OL,10,Fin the village of Whitehead. A place
OL,11,Fshe should have felt safe.
OL,13,F"Alyson was a much-loved mother,
OL,14,Fgrandmother and sister. The entire
OL,15,Ffamily has suffered a huge loss made
OL,16,Fonly the more agonising by the cruel
OL,17,Fway in which her life was actually
OL,18,Ftaken.
