OL,3,CEx-partner jailed for 20 years for
OL,4,CAlyson Nelson murder
OL,6,F"William Finlay and Alyson had
OL,7,Fpreviously been in a relationship
OL,8,Fwhich had ended over a year before the
OL,9,Ffatal stabbing even took place.
OL,11,F"As a result, William Finlay is the
OL,12,Ffirst person in Northern Ireland to be
OL,13,Fconvicted and sentenced for murder
OL,14,Fwhich has been aggravated by domestic
OL,15,Fabuse under new legislation.
OL,17,F"I know that Alyson's loving family
OL,18,Fare heartbroken and my thoughts, and
OL,19,Fthe thoughts of our entire team,
OL,20,Fremain with them today."
